DESCRIPTION: Contains definitions of the columns to be displayed in the Onboarding grid on the Connected Onboarding home page. 
It can be used to add, remove, modify, and rearrange columns.


DEFAULT BEHAVIOR: Returns a list of grid columns:
  Onboarding
  Status Icon - Funded, Active, etc
  Customer
  Owner 



CUSTOMIZATION STEPS: 
Add, remove, modify, or rearrange grid columns using a!gridColumn(). We recommend that you do not have any 
heavy rule executions like queries in the "value" section of an a!gridColumn(), as they evaluate once per row. 
For additional reference data, pass the type into the local variable local!refData query.
Note: fv!row is of type AS_IO_OnboardingRequest_SyncedRecordType called in AS_IO_CPS_myOnboardingsGrid.
Note: The estimated funding date and actual funding date columns are not customizable and are not included in this rule


PARAMETERS: 
i18nData: internationalization column labels


EXPECTED RETURN TYPE: List of a!gridColumn()

*/
